   * See also:
   *
   *    lu
   *
   * @param {Matrix | Array} A    A two dimensional matrix or array 
   * for which to get the QR decomposition.
   *
   * @return {{Q: Array | Matrix, R: Array | Matrix}} Q: the orthogonal
   * matrix and R: the upper triangular matrix
